text: The Grant (formerly One Museum Park West) is the companion structure to One Museum Park in the Near South Side community area (neighborhood) in Chicago, Illinois, USA. It is located at the north end of the Central Station development. It stands at 181 metres (594 ft). ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website *Emporis listing *Prairie District Neighborhood Alliance website Category:Skyscrapers in Chicago Category:2010 establishments in Illinois
